         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located in the Faculty of Yale College Records (RU 541).   The records consist of memoranda and reports documenting the activities and operations of the Faculty of Yale College. Included are minutes from meetings of the faculty and executive committee, committee reports, attendance books, committee membership lists, and financial papers.   Note: Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-C (YRG 9-C), Records of Yale College officers and faculty.</p>
         <p>HM 217 only consists of faculty minutes (1807-1957)</p>  
